      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">8.1104</ph> Contract clauses.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Insert the following clauses in solicitations and contracts
for leasing of motor vehicles, unless the motor vehicles are leased in
foreign countries:</p>
         <ol id="d521e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d536e12" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> The
clause at <xref href="FAR-i1062379.dita#i1062379"
                        base="i1062379"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.208-4</xref>, Vehicle Lease
Payments.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d536e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> The clause
at <xref href="FAR-i1062392.dita#i1062392"
                        base="i1062392"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.208-5</xref>, Condition of
Leased Vehicles.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d536e28" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph> The clause
at <xref href="FAR-i1062403.dita#i1062403"
                        base="i1062403"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.208-6</xref>, Marking of Leased
Vehicles.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d536e36" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph> A clause
substantially the same as the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1062413.dita#i1062413"
                        base="i1062413"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.208-7</xref>, Tagging of Leased
Vehicles, for vehicles leased over 60 days (see subpart B of <ph outputclass="CFR" class="- topic/ph ">41 CFR part 102</ph>-34).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d536e47" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph> The provisions
and clauses prescribed elsewhere in the FAR for solicitations and
contracts for supplies when a fixed-price contract is contemplated,
but excluding-</p>
               <ol id="d521e74" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d536e53" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> The clause at <xref href="FAR-i1063103.dita#i1063103"
                              base="i1063103"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.211-16</xref>, Variation in
Quantity;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d536e61" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> The clause
at <xref href="FAR-i1049385.dita#i1049385"
                              base="i1049385"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.232-1</xref>, Payments;</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d536e69" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph> The clause
at <xref href="FAR-i1055699.dita#i1055699"
                              base="i1055699"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.222-20</xref>, Contracts for
Materials, Supplies, Articles, and <ph rev="FAC 2020-06 June 5, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-007?>Equipment;<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 8.1104 by removing from paragraph (e)(3) “Exceeding $15,000”.?></ph> and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d536e82" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph> The clause
at <xref href="FAR-i1047139.dita#i1047139"
                              base="i1047139"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.246-16</xref>, Responsibility
for Supplies.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
